Class StepProfiler

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.diffplug.common.debug.StepProfiler

  • public class StepProfiler
extends Object
    Profiles the various steps of code. Example usage: ```java public static final StepProfiler stepProfiler = new StepProfiler(LapTimer.createNonWrap2Sec()); ... public void methodWhichNeedsProfiling(); stepProfiler.startStep("A"); ... stepProfiler.startStep("B"); } ...
